snippet.title: Mario Bros. Special (PC-8801) Gameplay - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
Gameplay demonstration of Hudson's 1984 NEC PC-8801 game, Mario Bros Special, from http://www.nintendocomplete.com/hudsons-pc/

If you'd like to see a write-up on Mario Bros. Special as well as Hudson's other Japanese exclusive officially licensed PC games, hit up the link above!
